('foundation', 'common-vocabulary', 'beginner', 'What action do you do to make a bed neat?', '["Make", "Unmake", "Sleep", "Sit"]', 0, 'Make (a bed) means to arrange sheets and pillows. Household chore verb.', 'medium'),
('foundation', 'common-vocabulary', 'beginner', 'Which verb means "to move something towards you"?', '["Pull", "Push", "Throw", "Drop"]', 0, 'Pull means to draw something closer. Directional action verb.', 'medium'),
