('foundation', 'common-vocabulary', 'beginner', 'What emotion describes feeling confused and unable to decide?', '["Bewildered", "Clear", "Decisive", "Focused"]', 0, 'Bewildered means confused or puzzled. Advanced emotion vocabulary.', 'medium'),
